{"tid":730531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【放榜勵志名人】艷麗少女會考6 分 毅然踏上星途闖政壇 終成樂壇翹楚","createTime":"2018-07-05T13:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T22:32:27.000Z","uid":24160,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d173e13c1d60f5adb1db4ba914678d1a02c5b6fb","tid":730531,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:05:57.000Z","msg":"汪明荃會考肥佬踏星途<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20050811/Article_ent/11ec2p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20050811%2FArticle_ent%2F11ec2p4.jpg&h=68410bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪明荃昨日表示會考只是人生一個階段而已。<br />\n<br />\n汪明荃（阿姐）昨日到港台接受《開心日報》訪問，適逢昨日中學會考放榜，有十優狀元大唱生日歌恭賀本月底生日的阿姐。 <br />\n阿姐自爆當年會考曾「肥佬」，她說：「我差一科先及格，好灰心，當時諗住讀夜校，但最後搵到工就入娛樂圈。」阿姐表示會考不是人生的盡頭，只是人生的一個階段。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161106/large/1478437696_4e40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161106%2Flarge%2F1478437696_4e40.jpg&h=72f08357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n盼政府助新光<br />\n對於新光戲院可以繼續經營，阿姐坦言現時新光仍欠千多萬元裝修費，她說：「呢個係好大數目，希望政府可以幫手，因為靠粵劇義演好難籌得到錢。」 <br />\n此外，本月二十八日是阿姐生日，到時她會與男友羅家英及一班朋友到歐洲遊玩，下星期便會起程，玩足兩星期，所以阿姐今年未能和歌迷共度生日。 <br />\n採訪、攝影：駱華齡"},{"pid":"bce1e14d9d44701936f41e61c85a6e42d09433c2","tid":730531,"uid":6604,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"明荃之友光速報到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60fac2072aa8cbc951e50068797fc1f105a469f","tid":730531,"uid":3037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T13:19:58.000Z","msg":"Wah<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b77736838f5302eb1b74f7dcf20357d6